                        <head><hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Beaupré</persName> to
                                the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Buenos
                                        Aires</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-02-08"><hi rend="italic">February 8,
                                1905</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>(Mr. Beaupré reports that the insurrection has been suppressed.)</p>
